If the process exits with a non-zero value, the Stream will provide all lines up to termination and then throw an exception.

trans-unit.source: Steppers have an iterator-like interface with methods hasStep and nextStep(). The difference to iterators - and the reason Stepper is not a subtype of Iterator - is that there are hand-specialized variants of Stepper for Int, Long and Double (IntStepper, etc.). These enable iterating over collections holding unboxed primitives (e.g., Arrays, scala.jdk.Accumulators) without boxing the elements.
trans-unit.target: 步进器具有类似迭代器的接口，其中包含方法 hasStep 和 nextStep() 。与迭代器的区别-以及 Stepper 不是 Iterator 的子类型的原因-是有针对 Int ， Long 和 Double （IntStepper等）的 Stepper 手工特殊变体。这些使您可以遍历包含未装箱原语（例如Arrays，scala.jdk.Accumulator）的集合，而无需将元素装箱。
